{"tid":22390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人大釋法】說好的廣大市民支持呢？嶺大民調：反多過撐","createTime":"2016-12-04T12:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T16:46:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53dbab938fb03c9d5466dcd4426448d73f502cb4","tid":22390,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:00:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161204/large/1480839378_7c0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161204%2Flarge%2F1480839378_7c0b.png&h=2b1ff3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 為阻止多名非建制派議員繼續擔任立法會議員，特首梁振英借律政司入稟，司法覆核他們的議員資格；人大委員長張德江更未待本港法院宣判，主動提出釋法，被指向法院施壓，遭不少人強烈質疑。雖然左報、親中政黨甚至張德江本人，均一直聲稱釋法「獲廣大市民支持」，但傳媒委託嶺大的民意調查指，只有39.3%受訪市民贊成今次釋法，反對則有42.6%，相差只有約3個百分點，並無壓倒性民意。<br />\n<br />\nnow新聞台委託嶺南大學公共管治研究部，在上月底用電話訪問1,052名市民，發現年紀越大的人，越贊成今次釋法；50歲以上的人，46.5%贊成釋法，反對有30.9%；30至49歲的，反對釋法的比率增至45.4%，贊成的跌至40.1%；18至29歲的年輕受訪者，不贊成的多達64.4%，贊成只有20.7%。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，沒有大專或以上學歷的市民，贊成釋法的比率較反對多，但有大專或以上學歷的，則有逾半人不贊成釋法。負責調查的李彭廣表示，今次釋法涉及民族大義，蓋過以往市民對釋法的反感。至於特首梁振英的支持度，在釋法後稍微上升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161204/56003119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161204%2F56003119&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bdb28bd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161204%2F56003119&h=7124457f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161204/56003119</a>"},{"pid":"140c32ebc5f50172f32b9a5c9bf2dd17dd84c94e","tid":22390,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:01:58.000Z","msg":"年紀越大，沒有大專或以上學歷的市民，越贊成今次釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b712590e00e4b62c344418dcf5a3aa4791ccc0d","tid":22390,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"個20%咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc2a733f4d5454148edf4cfa61a4d7a40231f0f","tid":22390,"uid":47210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"真係得班廢中廢老支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e840acba6bf3ffbbb0b941f2c1be432af832af","tid":22390,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個20%咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你行入去一轉就明白。<br />\n<br />\n我好驚訝得20%。"},{"pid":"d5bf8d9ab4d6bf167d535b6ba48e1d6ebb2a68c7","tid":22390,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個20%咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你行入去一轉就明白。<br />\n<br />\n我好驚訝得20%。</blockquote><br />\n純粹睇我自己既社交圏子<br />\n呢個年紀既人又真係得20%係藍絲<br />\n而且大部份都係紀律部隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7cf2d8d13420b154e2e292cf9abd53b5a27aef","tid":22390,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"全港贊成有40%都夠on9啦..."},{"pid":"369aa278b55c578b5d8ec284bf09d5ed58ac5077","tid":22390,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"人民鬥人民"},{"pid":"8cfb173c6076ea521fd8145a1341a3f52cc83b8b","tid":22390,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T12:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個20%咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把新香港人啦"},{"pid":"f7b70eb3a06b8b6cf23a82e0b6f3959682aa85b7","tid":22390,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個20%咩人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" cl